				<Text Type="text">
					&lt;p&gt;Some of the highest ranked breweries in Italy include:&lt;/p&gt;

					&lt;ul&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Le Baladin (Highly recommended but these might be harder to find)&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Panil Birra Artigianale&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Revelation Cat Craft Brewing&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Birra del Borgo&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Birrificio Toccalmatto&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Birrificio Lambrate&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;Maltus Faber&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;/ul&gt;

					&lt;p&gt;Note that in Europe there aren't as many mega breweries so local craft brewing is much more popular.  You should look for a local brewery for fresher and more easily accessible (in terms of cost and rarity). &lt;/p&gt;

